mmoottdd -- System Administration

File that holds message of the day
/eettcc/mmoottdd

The file mmoottdd holds the message  of the day.  Its contents are displayed by
the script /eettcc/pprrooffiillee, which is executed whenever you log in.

Only the superuser can alter the contents of this file.

